children.name: Validate user able to Credit Invoice
Validate user able to Credit Invoice
Given User launches Epro url and login with valid from Sheetname "Epro_details" and Rownum 1
And User go to Credit Invoice page and create a Credit Invoice
Then User will send the Final credit invoice
